Public schema tables (5 total), all with RLS enabled and currently 0 rows:

- **multiplayer_sessions**: PK `id` (uuid, default `gen_random_uuid()`); FKs `story_version_id → story_versions.id`, `host_id → users.id`; key columns include `status` enum (`pending|active|completed`, default `pending`), `settings`/`session_state` jsonb, `version` int default 0, timestamps.
- **saves**: PK `id` (uuid, default `gen_random_uuid()`); FKs `story_id → stories.id`, `user_id → users.id`; includes `save` jsonb, `mode` text default `solo` with check (`solo|multiplayer`), timestamps.
- **stories**: PK `id` (uuid, default `gen_random_uuid()`); unique `slug`; FK `created_by → users.id` (nullable); includes `title`, optional `summary`, timestamps.
- **story_versions**: PK `id` (uuid, default `gen_random_uuid()`); FK `story_id → stories.id`; includes `status` enum (`draft|published`, default `draft`), `outline` jsonb, optional `published_at`, plus `component_lock` jsonb, `engine_range`, `shell` jsonb default `{"key":"shell.ebook"}`, `theme`, timestamps.
- **users**: PK `id` (uuid); FK `id → auth.users.id`; includes optional `username`, `avatar_url`, timestamps.
